(873, 191, 'why_us_people_about-1', '<p>Principal Consultant Scaling business & Start-ups</p>\r\n<p class=\"about-people\">Entrepreneur with a proven track record of building high performing teams. Andy has built and led teams focused on providing exceptional experiences for their clients, always with a focus on personal development and human transformation. Andy has founded, lead and scaled multiple 7 & 8 figure businesses across varying industries. In hindsight his greatest achievements were placing the right person in the right role, and watching them transform as their career becomes an avenue of personal development. Andy brings his CEO experience- a deep understanding of organizations, their structure and how the right culture leads to growth to the DNA of the Elton Mayo\'s vision. Andy looks forward to helping you or your organization thrive & grow.</p>'),
(874, 191, '_why_us_people_about-1', 'field_6450fe1aa3ced'),
(875, 191, 'why_us_people_about-2', '<p>Principal Consultant Corporate Services</p>\r\n<p class=\"about-people\">With a varied background in HR, Sales, and Business Management Fady always had a passion for building thriving teams. Spending about a decade within HR across multiple industries provided an understanding for the importance of implementing a clear and\r\npractical working culture if an organisation is to live out its mission and ultimately it\'s vision to stakeholders and potentially the world. Having built, operated, and sold multiple businesses contributed to acquiring a skillset in building teams that are both individually and collectively aligned to the business\'s culture, one of the founding blocks to creating an environment for high performing teams. Fady is a passionate and determined professional providing recruitment solutions and talent acquisition strategies for your organisation.</p>'),
